<subSubSection pageId="67" pageNumber="775" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="67.[1373,2578,712,984]" pageId="67" pageNumber="775">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1374,1727,795,824]" pageId="67" pageNumber="775">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not yet assessed on The [UCN Red List. Current population trend of the Yunnan Giant Flying Squirrel is unknown. More surveys and basic research on its distribution, population status, and natural history are needed to better understand threats and useful conservation action.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
